---
import LandingLayout from "../layouts/LandingLayout.astro";
import girl from "../assets/images/girl.jpg";
import Image from "astro/components/Image.astro";
---

<LandingLayout>
	<div class="flex space-x-4 py-4">
		<Image
			src={girl}
			alt="Anime girl."
			width={150}
			class="object-contain"
		/>
		<div class="sm:p-4 sm:space-y-2">
			<h1 class="">Hi, I'm Devin.</h1>
			<p class="">check out my:</p>
			<div
				class="sm:flex sm:space-x-5 grid grid-cols-2 gap-3 underline"
			>
				<a
					href="mailto:devinrankin@proton.me"
					target="_blank"
					class="hover:bg-foreground hover:text-background">contact</a
				>
				<a
					href="https://github.com/devinrankin"
					target="_blank"
					class="hover:bg-foreground hover:text-background">github</a
				>
				<a
					href="https://linkedin.com/in/devinrankin0"
					target="_blank"
					class="hover:bg-foreground hover:text-background">linkedin</a
				>
				<a
					href="https://discord.com/users/295721632079675392"
					target="_blank"
					class="hover:bg-foreground hover:text-background">discord</a
				>
				<a
					href="https://instagram.com/devinrxnkin"
					class="hover:bg-foreground hover:text-background">instagram</a
				>
			</div>
			<p>
				or my blog <a
					href="/blog"
					class="underline hover:bg-foreground hover:text-background">here</a
				>
			</p>
		</div>
	</div>
	<hr class="text-foreground border-t-2 border-foreground" />
	<article class="flex justify-between md:flex-row flex-col">
		<div class="flex-1 border-2 border-foreground p-4">
			<h2># Experience</h2>
			<p>! This list is summarized. For more information on my work history, please see <a href="/resume-rankin.pdf" class="underline hover:text-background hover:bg-foreground text-nowrap">my resume</a>.</p>
			<ul class="mt-8 ml-2 space-y-4 list-disc">
				<li>
					<span class="text-[#ac9e9e] text-sm font-thin"
						>Feb 2024 - Present</span
					>
					<h3>
						<a
							href="https://owlhacks.com"
							class="hover:bg-foreground hover:text-background underline underline-offset-4"
						>
							Lead Developer @ Owlhacks
						</a>
					</h3>
				</li>
				<li>
					<span class="text-foreground-dull text-sm font-thin">Aug 2023 - May 2024</span>
					<h3>CS Peer Tutor & Operating Systems Teaching Assistant</h3>
				</li>
				<li>
					<span class="text-foreground-dull text-sm font-thin">May 2023 - Jul 2023</span>
					<h3>
						<a
							href="https://coventry.com"
							class="hover:bg-foreground hover:text-background underline underline-offset-4"
						>
							Software Eng. Intern @ Coventry Life Settlements
						</a>
					</h3>
				</li>
				<li>
					<span class="text-foreground-dull text-sm font-thin">Jan 2023 - May 2023</span>
					<h3>Program Design & Abstraction Teaching Assistant</h3>
				</li>
			</ul>
		</div>
		<div class="flex-1 border-2 border-foreground p-4">
			<h2># Projects</h2>
			<p>! Click on the project title to visit their respective repository.</p>
			<ul class="mt-8 ml-2 space-y-4 w-3/4 experience list-disc">
				<li>
					<h3>
						<a
							href="https://github.com/CIS-3207-F22/project-2-linux-shell-devinrankin/"
							class="hover:text-background hover:bg-foreground underline underline-offset-4"
							target="_blank">Shell</a
						>
					</h3>
					<p>A UNIX shell clone written in C.</p>
				</li>
				<li>
					<h3>
						<a
							href="https://github.com/devinrankin/c8-emu"
							class="hover:text-background hover:bg-foreground underline underline-offset-4"
							target="_blank">c8-emu</a
						>
					</h3>
					<p>
						A CHIP-8 beginner emulator project written in <span
							class="whitespace-nowrap">C++</span
						>.
					</p>
					<li>
						<h3>
							<a
								href="https://github.com/devinrankin/gbc-emu"
								class="hover:text-background hover:bg-foreground underline underline-offset-4"
								target="_blank">gbCPP</a
							>
						</h3>
						<p>
							A GameBoy Color Emulator written in <span
								class="whitespace-nowrap">C++</span
							>. The most fun project I've worked on by far.
						</p>
					</li>
					<li>
						<h3>
							<a
								href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=iiHYFNoYW9U"
								class="hover:bg-foreground hover:text-background underline underline-offset-4"
								target="_blank">Inquiry</a
							>
						</h3>
						<p>
							Inquiry, a multi-platform real-time messaging app that a friend
							and I conceptualized during a hackathon in 2023, is for students
							to ask questions and show reaction during lectures without the
							fear of public opinion. Written in Typescript & HTML with React,
							Electron, and a PostgreSQL backend.
						</p>
					</li>
				</li>
			</ul>
		</div>
	</article>
	<div class="border-2 border-foreground p-4 flex items-center justify-center">
		<p>「向日葵。真夏に咲き誇る地上の太陽、それはまるで永遠に照り続けるかのように。けれど、場気な向日葵も夏が終われば枯れていく・・・」</p>
	</div>
</LandingLayout>
